{"tid":41253,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇另一半唔記得自己生日","createTime":"2016-12-15T18:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T01:11:32.000Z","uid":63016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e7a6d83432fe34fd1e84d7e30305e37cbdefb944","tid":41253,"uid":63016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:00:32.000Z","msg":"一齊兩年幾 自己上個月生日 男朋友唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係第二日 尷尷尬尬咁同佢講返佢先知<br />\n本身自己都唔會對生日好大期望 其實生日咪又係咁過~<br />\n只不過另一半唔記得就點都有啲不是味兒<br />\n你地又覺得點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果男/女朋友唔記得自己生日"},{"pid":"8bf100c1de505655c4f48780a7dc350e7e6b1e25","tid":41253,"uid":24052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:03:13.000Z","msg":"我上年生日過左兩個月後，我老婆先記起。<br />\n<br />\n利申：結婚十二年"},{"pid":"ac1ef74eedca6b4d33b73ad1ddf2f7fcfbdd68c6","tid":41253,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:16:28.000Z","msg":"睇佢本身份人係點<br />\n個個都唔記<br />\n冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得異性朋友生日<br />\n係唔記得你生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就自己考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa96f60ae4b8dbaf347f23d56613af1120161e4","tid":41253,"uid":51134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:22:03.000Z","msg":"唔記得好過記錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df2add06011f244c9f8c779db5336e6136e880e","tid":41253,"uid":63016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T03:50:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔記得好過記錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢都試過記錯呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 記錯做前後一兩日"},{"pid":"d669a46ee0bbc53aa8f45f8ef83e6cf79cc9eddf","tid":41253,"uid":66305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T03:55:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">帽事既</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f72cf273f91d14d8cbe2d0f6ffbef8647f64ead8","tid":41253,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T03:57:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔記得好過記錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢都試過記錯呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 記錯做前後一兩日</blockquote><br />\n一齊兩年即係無記啱過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b3c0771528966102085ae0989d8f768e4cecf36","tid":41253,"uid":63016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:34:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔記得好過記錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢都試過記錯呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 記錯做前後一兩日</blockquote><br />\n一齊兩年即係無記啱過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係o既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊之前個個生日佢打過段千字文比我 個陣感動到喊 我係好易感動o既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後一齊左 第一個生日就就咁一句生日快樂啦 咁我都冇咩o野 <br />\n記錯係有次我地傾計講起 佢話 你xx號生日嘛 個下都幾sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c34aa4ddbd0efdeb70a9eed7cba270a2255777d2","tid":41253,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:43:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔記得好過記錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢都試過記錯呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 記錯做前後一兩日</blockquote><br />\n一齊兩年即係無記啱過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係o既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊之前個個生日佢打過段千字文比我 個陣感動到喊 我係好易感動o既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後一齊左 第一個生日就就咁一句生日快樂啦 咁我都冇咩o野 <br />\n記錯係有次我地傾計講起 佢話 你xx號生日嘛 個下都幾sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n外人睇其實幾誇張<br />\n不過你地平時可能相處得開心就唔知啦"},{"pid":"43b6a66ba462488c160e6eb87944cc7d800b45e4","tid":41253,"uid":49250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:50:19.000Z","msg":"飛得"},{"pid":"79e66e797880f823c18d85d7bd51fb5bbc0f446d","tid":41253,"uid":61049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:54:44.000Z","msg":"冇咩所謂<br />\n反正都係自己過冇人會記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe413cc0abe824033875a015ce1cb02428725074","tid":41253,"uid":63016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T01:02:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n外人睇其實幾誇張<br />\n不過你地平時可能相處得開心就唔知啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見面個時係幾開心o既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但有時佢做o既o野我真係好難接受<br />\n我地一星期見一次 唔見o既日子靠wtsapp溝通<br />\n但好多時 每日都只係得幾個msg 佢唔覆我 或者有時佢隔好耐先覆 其實好無癮..<br />\n我知o既就只係知佢返緊學 幾時上堂落堂 做過咩 返左屋企都唔會知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢幾日佢唔係香港 琴日同佢講我病左到而家都未應我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢都意識到自己有呢個問題 都有主動同我講過 但講完根本就冇改過<br />\n<br />\n有時聽到啲人話 一齊幾年仲會日日傾電話 都會有啲羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 哪怕係幾分鐘都好 <br />\n我唔會要求佢咁 只係唔好斷聯絡我已經覺得ok<br />\n溝通真係好重要"},{"pid":"2c4f22af500db54a4230b141aab1ef5f23fbd700","tid":41253,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T01:07:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n外人睇其實幾誇張<br />\n不過你地平時可能相處得開心就唔知啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見面個時係幾開心o既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但有時佢做o既o野我真係好難接受<br />\n我地一星期見一次 唔見o既日子靠wtsapp溝通<br />\n但好多時 每日都只係得幾個msg 佢唔覆我 或者有時佢隔好耐先覆 其實好無癮..<br />\n我知o既就只係知佢返緊學 幾時上堂落堂 做過咩 返左屋企都唔會知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢幾日佢唔係香港 琴日同佢講我病左到而家都未應我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢都意識到自己有呢個問題 都有主動同我講過 但講完根本就冇改過<br />\n<br />\n有時聽到啲人話 一齊幾年仲會日日傾電話 都會有啲羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 哪怕係幾分鐘都好 <br />\n我唔會要求佢咁 只係唔好斷聯絡我已經覺得ok<br />\n溝通真係好重要</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢d 相處方式無話啱定錯<br />\n最緊要雙方有無共識同舒唔舒服<br />\n但睇你字𥚃行間明顯你係唔想咁落去<br />\n建議你同你bf傾傾好d"},{"pid":"b78560fd1c3c1b764e2d3d17506b3ccc2b5793b3","tid":41253,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T01:11:32.000Z","msg":"記得其他人生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}